Southern Man
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a strong silent male of the southern South Island, a stereotype popularised by (Speights)beer advertisements.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
